{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-097-098-a-small-blue-case",
    "title": "Lesson 97: A small blue case",
    "audioFilename": "097&098－A Small Blue Case.mp3",
    "duration": 93.78,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.27,
      "end": 1.87,
      "text": "Lesson 97.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第97课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 2.75,
      "end": 4.73,
      "text": "A Small Blue Case.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "一只蓝色小箱子。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 7.26,
      "end": 11.2,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 12.94,
      "end": 13.8,
      "text": "Does Mr. Hall",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "霍尔先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 14.16,
      "end": 16.06,
      "text": "get his case back?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "拿回自己的箱子了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 18.24,
      "end": 23.32,
      "text": "I left a suitcase on the train to London the other day.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "前几天我把一只手提箱落在了去伦敦的火车上。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 24.3,
      "end": 26.4,
      "text": "Can you describe it, sir?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您能描述一下吗，先生？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 27.38,
      "end": 32.46,
      "text": "It's a small blue case, and it's got a zip.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "是一只蓝色小箱子，带拉链。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 34.14,
      "end": 39.72,
      "text": "There's a label on the handle with my name and address on it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "提手上有个标签，写着我的姓名和地址。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 40.36,
      "end": 42.2,
      "text": "Is this case yours?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这只箱子是您的吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 43.1,
      "end": 44.98,
      "text": "No, that's not mine.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "不，那只不是我的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 45.88,
      "end": 47.74,
      "text": "What about this one?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这只呢？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 48.3,
      "end": 50.22,
      "text": "This one's got a label.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这只上面有标签。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 51.48,
      "end": 53.14,
      "text": "Let me see it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "让我看看。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 53.9,
      "end": 56.2,
      "text": "What's your name and address?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您的姓名和地址是什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 57.68,
      "end": 61.74,
      "text": "David Hall, 83 Bridge Street.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "戴维·霍尔，桥街83号。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 62.9,
      "end": 63.34,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "没错。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 64.66,
      "end": 65.08,
      "text": "D. N.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "D. N."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 65.56,
      "end": 68.4,
      "text": "Hall, 83 Bridge Street.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "霍尔，桥街83号。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 70.04,
      "end": 72.62,
      "text": "Three pounds, fifty pence, please.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "请付3英镑50便士。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 73.86,
      "end": 74.88,
      "text": "Here you are.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "给您。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 75.54,
      "end": 76.16,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "谢谢。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 76.92,
      "end": 77.28,
      "text": "Hey!",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "嘿！"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 78.14,
      "end": 79.08,
      "text": "What's the matter?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "怎么了？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s025",
      "start": 79.08,
      "end": 83.18,
      "text": "This case doesn't belong to me.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这只箱子不是我的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s026",
      "start": 84.46,
      "end": 86.92,
      "text": "You've given me the wrong case.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您给错箱子了。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
